                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>A fair will be presented Feb. 22 by the ladies for the Company; much of
                    article illegible.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>2</column>
                <head>That Convention</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p>"Sam, we were told, however, had no voice in the affair,--poor, neglected
                        Sam, who but a few short years since, stalked so vauntingly in Virginia and
                        gave shelter, consolation and comfort to so many Whigs."</p>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Stuart</ln>
