            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>Opposition to Imposition</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p>"Then comes the great strength of this opposition,---the Black Republicans,
                        the Abolitionists, and all the isms of the north, the Fanny Wright men, the
                        anti-renters, the Mormons....They should have learned wisdom from the past,
                        and remembered how the yeomanry of the South, and especially of Virginia,
                        tracked the wily Sam through all his windings, and denounced him as a humbug
                        and imposter, in spite of his disguises."</p>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Article praises the Democratic party for its nationality and cheers the
                    party for taking the Constitution as its guide. Argues that the Democrats are
                    the only real national party and blasts elements of the Opposition.</summary>
                <note>aubrowser/rvfeb59.html#2.19a</note>
            </div>
